            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "mGkbLuXtisEvFNNs",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp",
            "name": "Fastening Leap",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The dig-widget Leaps up 20 feet onto a creature or object and attempts a corkscrew Strike against it. If the Strike damages the target, the dig-widget attaches to the target (typically to the back of a creature). This is similar to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.bestiary-ability-glossary-srd.Item.Grab]{Grabbing} the creature, but the dig-widget moves with that creature rather than holding it in place. While attached, the dig-widget can't use its corkscrew. The dig-widget can be @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Shove]{Shoved} off, or it can detach itself with an Interact action.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": []
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "EigEgS2SCI89hnu6",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Grind Bones",
            "sort": 700000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> A grinder-widget adjacent to the millstone in area <strong>C41</strong> has a creature @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Grabbed]</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The grinder-widget attaches pliers to one of the millstone's handles and Strides around it, causing the Grabbed character to be painfully ground and pulped by the stone. The ground character must attempt a @Check[reflex|dc:23|options:damaging-effect,inflicts:clumsy] save with the following results.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The character is unaffected and automatically Escapes from the grapple.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The character takes @Damage[(1d8+2)[bludgeoning]] damage and then automatically Escapes from the grapple.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The character takes @Damage[(2d8+2)[bludgeoning]] damage and becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1} for 1 hour from wrenched and sprained limbs; the character remains grappled by the grinder-widget.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but @Damage[(4d8+2)[bludgeoning]] damage and clumsy 1 for 24 hours.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "manipulate",
                        "move"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
